&lt;p&gt;
	As the owner of a small artisan chilli product business with a strong track record of food safety and quality, I would like to provide context around our most recent food hygiene rating.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	Prior to this inspection, our business proudly maintained a &lt;strong&gt;consistent Food Hygiene Rating of 5&lt;/strong&gt; while operating from a registered home kitchen. We made the decision to invest in the long-term future of the business by upgrading to a &lt;strong&gt;dedicated, purpose-built food production workshop&lt;/strong&gt;. This move was made to meet increased demand, improve efficiency, and maintain our commitment to the highest possible standards of hygiene and food safety.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	We recognise that transitioning to a new facility naturally brings fresh inspections and updated compliance requirements. Following the inspection, we received valuable feedback from the Environmental Health Officer. &lt;strong&gt;All recommendations made have now been fully implemented and adhered to.&lt;/strong&gt; We have also reviewed and strengthened our food safety management systems to ensure continued compliance with best practices.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	We remain absolutely committed to maintaining the highest hygiene standards and regaining our &lt;strong&gt;Food Hygiene Rating of 5&lt;/strong&gt; at the next eligible re-inspection, which will be possible &lt;strong&gt;11 months&lt;/strong&gt; from the initial visit.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	Thank you for your continued support as we grow and improve our facilities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	Sincerely,&lt;br /&gt;
	&lt;strong&gt;Chilli Gold team&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
